    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years. It runs super smoothly, looks great, and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a reliable, honest ride that still has plenty of life left, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
