    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed double VANOS system to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The drivetrain features a factory M-variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and the installation of Bilstein B16 coilovers for improved damping characteristics and roll-center geometry. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals remain stout and track-ready.",
