    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i xDrive, a vehicle that perfectly balances executive luxury with spirited performance. The exterior, finished in Sophisto Grey Metallic, retains a deep, mirror-like shine. While the body is straight and the paint is original, there are a few minor, unavoidable stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim, consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the Mocha Dakota leather seats are firm and free of cracks, and the cabin remains smoke-free and fresh. All technological features\u2014including the head-up display, gesture control, and the premium Harman Kardon sound system\u2014are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged inline-six runs flawlessly. I have adhered strictly to the manufacturer's service schedule, with a comprehensive inspection and oil service completed just last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly, and requires nothing but a new driver. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
