      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road. It runs super smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
