    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Shifting is handled by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M-differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its composure via a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. This example has already received essential subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, addressing the platform's primary mechanical concerns. While the exterior reflects an honest patina appropriate for its condition, the hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and the engine\u2019s compression is within factory spec. A mechanically robust specimen for the purist.",
